properties.headline: FLOODING MACQUARIE PASS Illawarra Highway
properties.diversions:
Light vehicles: via Jamberoo Mountain Rd and should allow an extra 10 minutes travel time between Robertson and Albion Park.

Heavy vehicles: via the Hume Hwy, Picton Rd and the M1 Princes Mwy and should allow an additional 30 minutes travel time between the Hume Mwy and Albion Park.

properties.headline: FLOODING MOREE TO BOGGABILLA Newell Highway
properties.otherAdvice: This information will be updated when conditions change. For information relating to Queensland road closures go to QLD traffic
properties.diversions:
Northbound motorists from Moree can use the Gwydir Hwy to Glen Innes to join the New England Hwy

Southbound motorists from Boggabilla can use theBruxner Hwy via Yetman to Warialda, then Gwydir Hwy.

These diversions are due to various flooding related road closures in Queensland.

properties.headline: FLOODING ROYAL NATIONAL PARK Audley Weir between Audley Road and Sir Bertram Stevens Drive
properties.otherAdvice:
Visitors are encouraged to check the Royal National Park local alerts for updates on precinct access.

This information will be updated when conditions change.
properties.diversions:
McKell Ave is also closed.

The only access to Royal National Park is via Stanwell Tops: M1 Princes Mwy, then Lawrence Hargrave Dr, Otford Rd and Lady Wakehurst Dr, to access Sir Bertram Stevens Dr.
